Welcome to my study space! I'm Lucia, a first-year PhD  student in [AI](https://phd-ai-society.di.unipi.it/) at [UniPi](https://www.unipi.it). 
My research interest in mostly about Representation Learning in NLP. 

Outside of research, my main hobbies are learning languages and bouldering 🧗
>  Here, I collect personal notes on various topics I’m learning. They’re written for me, but might be helpful to others, too. Enjoy reading!

